divs: Sighting DetailsStanding in my backyard looking into the sky (facing north) I noticed a bright white light moving across the sky from west to east. It was a very clear night (no haze or overcast). The light seemed to be at the hight of a commercial jet but being at night it was difficult to tell. As the light moved more directly overhead I saw a stream of green light project from one side. Seconds later a red boomerang shaped object appeared to the rear and to the left of the bright light. This continued until the object reached about 2:30 in the eastern sky. It then suddenly dissapeared.
